text: Planorbidella is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Neomphalidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Planorbidella include: * Planorbidella depressa Warén & Bouchet, 1993 * Planorbidella planispira (Warén & Bouchet, 1989) ==References== Category:Neomphalidae
title: Planorbidella
